svg.title: Miami Pattern-01
svg.text: By Melissa GutierrezMiami is seen either as a vacation city, a party town, or an inaccurate combination of both. Rarely, the perceptions are matched with the rich multicultural history proven to be influential to this day.This project illustrates a visual history of Miami that includes how architecture, demographics, cultural institutions, and cultural institutions have shaped the current landscape of the city.
